om: 0px; margin-left: 30pt; line-height: 12.6pt;"><span lang="EN-PH" style="font-size: 7pt; color: rgb(158, 158, 158);">1-If you are unable to attend, a substitute delegate will be welcome in your place.</span><span lang="EN-PH" style="font-size: 7pt; color: rgb(57, 61, 71);"><u></u><u></u></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 30pt; line-height: 12.6pt;"><span lang="EN-PH" style="font-size: 7pt; color: rgb(158, 158, 158);">2-Registrations cancelled more than 7 days before the Event are subject to a 200-Pound administration charge.</span><span lang="EN-PH" style="font-size: 7pt; color: rgb(57, 61, 71);"><u></u><u></u></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 30pt; line-height: 12.6pt;"><span lang="EN-PH" style="font-size: 7pt; color: rgb(158, 158, 158);">3-Registration fees for registrations cancelled 7 days or less before the Event must be paid in full.</span><span lang="EN-PH" style="font-size: 7pt; color: rgb(57, 61, 71);"><u></u><u></u></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 30pt; line-height: 12.6pt;"><span lang="EN-PH" style="font-size: 7pt; color: rgb(158, 158, 158);">4-Substitutions are welcome at any time.</span><span lang="EN-PH" style="font-size: 7pt; color: rgb(57, 61, 71);"><u></u><u></u></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 12.6pt;"><span lang="EN-PH" style="font-size: 7pt; color: rgb(158, 158, 158);">All registrations are subject to acceptance by (York British academy) which will be confirmed to you in writing.</span><span lang="EN-PH" style="font-size: 7pt; color: rgb(57, 61, 71);"><u></u><u></u></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 12.6pt;"><span lang="EN-PH" style="font-size: 7pt; color: rgb(158, 158, 158);">Due to unforeseen circumstances, the program may change and (York British academy) reserves the right to alter the venue and/or speakers or topics.</span><span lang="EN-PH" style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(57, 61, 71);"><u></u><u></u></span></p>
